title: The Innocents' Fountain

title: Mondial Hotel
description:
Mondial Hotel is a quality; comfortable hotel situated in a quiet area of the 9th arrondissement. The hotel's proximity to L'Opera and the many attractions of the grand boulevards; make it the perfect destination for both business and lesiure visitors to this vibrant city.

 	A peaceful location in the centre of Paris is difficult to find - but the Mondial has managed !. This 3-star hotel is located in a secluded and private side street, whilst being totally central to the tourist sites of Paris. Recently renovated, the hotel offers 60 rooms with bath/shower, hairdryer, satellite TV, telephone and private safety box. A continental breakfast buffet is available to all guests and is served in the traditional surroundings of the ground floor breakfast room. Recommended for location and value for money.
